00:19:11.441 --> 00:19:12.860 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No volverá a pasar.</c.bg_transparent>

327
00:19:12.943 --> 00:19:14.820 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Entonces, ¿qué harás con ella?</c.bg_transparent>

328
00:19:14.903 --> 00:19:17.322 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hasta que halle otra arma,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>quisiera seguir usándola.</c.bg_transparent>

329
00:19:17.906 --> 00:19:20.492 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Podría sumergirla en el agua
y ahogar a la criatura,</i></c.bg_transparent>

330
00:19:20.576 --> 00:19:22.369 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>luego desarmar la espada para sacarla,</i></c.bg_transparent>

331
00:19:22.452 --> 00:19:24.288 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>pero seguramente se pudriría.</i></c.bg_transparent>

332
00:19:24.371 --> 00:19:25.455 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Eso es desagradable.</i></c.bg_transparent>

333
00:19:25.539 --> 00:19:27.332 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Podemos esperar y ver qué pasa.</i></c.bg_transparent>

334
00:19:27.916 --> 00:19:30.794 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tú dijiste</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>que los monstruos son peligrosos.</c.bg_transparent>

335
00:19:31.420 --> 00:19:33.839 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No me olvidé de eso.</c.bg_transparent>

336
00:19:33.922 --> 00:19:35.841 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pero pensé que lo había neutralizado</c.bg_transparent>

337
00:19:35.924 --> 00:19:38.844 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>y que podía usarlo a mi favor.</c.bg_transparent>

338
00:19:38.927 --> 00:19:40.971 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pero no resultó.</c.bg_transparent>

339
00:19:41.054 --> 00:19:43.599 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Será imposible usar a un monstruo</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>mientras está vivo.</c.bg_transparent>

340
00:19:44.808 --> 00:19:46.518 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿A qué sabe?</c.bg_transparent>

341
00:19:47.144 --> 00:19:48.103 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Quieres probar?</c.bg_transparent>

342
00:19:48.187 --> 00:19:50.230 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Sí!</c.bg_transparent>

343
00:19:56.570 --> 00:20:01.033 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hay muchas puertas,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>pero solo dos llevan afuera.</c.bg_transparent>

344
00:20:01.116 --> 00:20:02.868 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No se preocupen por los ataques sorpresa.</c.bg_transparent>

345
00:20:07.706 --> 00:20:10.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Esta casa parece muy cómoda.</c.bg_transparent>

346
00:20:10.209 --> 00:20:12.377 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Es curioso el hecho</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>de que tenga siete baños.</c.bg_transparent>

347
00:20:12.461 --> 00:20:14.379 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Muy bien. Durmamos un poco aquí.</c.bg_transparent>

348
00:20:14.463 --> 00:20:15.839 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Hurra!</c.bg_transparent>

349
00:20:15.923 --> 00:20:18.091 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Hacía tanto que no dormía en una cama!</c.bg_transparent>

350
00:20:18.175 --> 00:20:20.677 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tendremos que usar</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>los sacos de dormir como mantas.</c.bg_transparent>

351
00:20:27.893 --> 00:20:30.479 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Perdón por irrumpir en tu casa.</c.bg_transparent>

352
00:20:30.562 --> 00:20:32.981 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nos iremos en cuanto descansemos un poco.</c.bg_transparent>

353
00:20:33.482 --> 00:20:34.900 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Qué pasa?</c.bg_transparent>

354
00:20:35.484 --> 00:20:36.526 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Debe ser una residente.</c.bg_transparent>

355
00:20:36.610 --> 00:20:37.903 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dice que nos deja quedarnos.</c.bg_transparent>

356
00:20:38.570 --> 00:20:39.404 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ya veo.</c.bg_transparent>

357
00:20:39.488 --> 00:20:40.572 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Genial.</c.bg_transparent>

358
00:20:41.990 --> 00:20:45.661 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nos faltan sacos de dormir,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>los compartiremos en el camino de regreso.</c.bg_transparent>

359
00:20:45.744 --> 00:20:49.373 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡No hemos dormido en la misma cama</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>desde la escuela!</c.bg_transparent>

360
00:20:49.456 --> 00:20:51.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Me pregunto si cabremos las dos.</c.bg_transparent>

361
00:20:51.792 --> 00:20:54.795 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He crecido mucho desde entonces.</c.bg_transparent>

362
00:20:54.878 --> 00:20:57.256 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Pequeña descarada!</c.bg_transparent>

363
00:20:59.132 --> 00:21:03.095 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Para mí, siempre serás mi niñita!</c.bg_transparent>

364
00:21:07.015 --> 00:21:09.184 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Me alegra mucho poder verte de nuevo.</c.bg_transparent>

365
00:21:10.602 --> 00:21:11.770 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A mí también.</c.bg_transparent>

366
00:21:14.940 --> 00:21:17.442 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Le daré las buenas noches a mi hermano.</c.bg_transparent>

367
00:21:21.488 --> 00:21:22.364 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Laios…</c.bg_transparent>

368
00:21:23.699 --> 00:21:24.700 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Falin…</c.bg_transparent>

369
00:21:32.791 --> 00:21:33.834 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Esta cicatriz…</c.bg_transparent>

370
00:21:33.917 --> 00:21:36.003 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hiciste algo imprudente, ¿verdad?</c.bg_transparent>

371
00:21:36.086 --> 00:21:36.962 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Por qué…?</c.bg_transparent>

372
00:21:41.300 --> 00:21:44.636 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Para que quede claro, tú fuiste la primera</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>en cometer una imprudencia.</c.bg_transparent>

373
00:21:44.720 --> 00:21:46.805 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Es tu culpa que las cosas resultaran así!</c.bg_transparent>

374
00:21:46.888 --> 00:21:47.723 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Qué?</c.bg_transparent>

375
00:21:47.806 --> 00:21:50.350 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡No vuelvas a hacer algo así!</c.bg_transparent>

376
00:21:51.059 --> 00:21:53.603 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ni siquiera recuerdo qué hice.</c.bg_transparent>

377
00:22:00.277 --> 00:22:01.778 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No lo volveré a hacer.</c.bg_transparent>

378
00:22:05.073 --> 00:22:06.992 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Buenas noches, Laios.</c.bg_transparent>

379
00:22:08.285 --> 00:22:09.995 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Buenas noches, Falin.</c.bg_transparent>

380
00:24:07.821 --> 00:24:11.950 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Subtítulos: Florencia Lago</c.bg_transparent>

